Supported chipsets :
---------------------------------
	* SiS 300 			(not tested)
	* SiS 540 			(not tested)
	* SiS 630 			(not tested)
	* SiS 730 			(not tested)
	* SiS 315 			(not tested)
	* SiS 325 			(not tested)
	* SiS 550 			(not tested)
	* SiS 650 			(not tested)
	* SiS 750 			(not tested)
	* SiS 330 ( Xabre )	(works)


Features :
----------------
	* Screen modes : 640x480 - 1600x1200 (16 BPP / 32 BPP)
	* Accelerated FillRect, DrawLine and BltBitmap
	* Hardware cursor

Changes :
----------------

