Installation :
-------------------
	* Source : ( you will need the binutils, gcc, make and packages )
		* Unpack the .tgz file to system/appserver/drivers/video
		* Type "make install"
		* Reboot
	* Binary :
		* Unpack the .tgz file
		* Type "sh install.sh"
		* Reboot





